descript.abstract: This file contains the locations and shapes of the buildings near the University of Oregon main campus in Eugene, Oregon. The data in this feature class was geocoded from the 2004 Aerial Photograph. This dataset is stored as an ArcSDE feature class in SQL.
descript.purpose: This dataset was created to assist in planning and mapping purposes
descript.supplinf: This dataset is stored in the UO InfoGraphics Campus Geodatabase - housed in 163 Condon.
